Base64.Encoder encoder = Base64.getEncoder();
getTeamID = String.valueOf(teamID);
String encodedTeamID = encoder.encodeToString(getTeamID.getBytes());


in volley android library add below lines for support long URL data
getTeamDataRequest.setRetryPolicy(new DefaultRetryPolicy(
1000000,
DefaultRetryPolicy.DEFAULT_MAX_RETRIES,
DefaultRetryPolicy.DEFAULT_BACKOFF_MULT));


Extra information 
Q : What is base64 ?
A : it is a combination of A-Z,a-z,0-9,+/
    + 26 (A-z) 
    + 26 (a-z)
    + 10 (0-9)
    + 2 (+/)
    ----------
    = 64 (Total Character supports for endcode) 



